  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Hirunika to C.I.D",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Mrs. Hirunika Premachandra has come to the Criminal Investigation Department today (20) to give a statement.",
        "According to a notice given by the Criminal Investigation Department to Mrs. Premachandra yesterday afternoon, she came to the Criminal Investigation Department this morning to give this statement.",
        "Before giving the statement, in response to a question raised by the media as to why the summons was made today, he stated that there is no mention of it in the letter he was summoned to and that he thinks it may be related to the struggle and that Ranil Rajapakse, who came to power with the help of the struggle, is the worst president ever born."
      ],
